      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "ギリギリ前の外"
    },
    {
      "start": 2.74,
      "end": 5.2,
      "text": "Avoids the KO",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "撃墜されないえつじ"
    },
    {
      "start": 5.2,
      "end": 7.12,
      "text": "137%",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "137%"
    },
    {
      "start": 7.12,
      "end": 9.08,
      "text": "Even for ZakRay, this is",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "これはいくらザクレイといえども"
    },
    {
      "start": 9.08,
      "end": 10.76,
      "text": "The set's getting pretty tight now, but",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "ちょっと厳しい試合になってきたが"
    },
    {
      "start": 10.76,
      "end": 12.18,
      "text": "Grabs",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "掴んで"
    },
    {
      "start": 12.18,
      "end": 13.94,
      "text": "Solid damage",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "手堅いダメージ"
    },
    {
      "start": 13.94,
      "end": 17.48,
      "text": "And that recovery from below...",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "この下からの復帰は"
    },
    {
      "start": 17.48,
      "end": 19.66,
      "text": "Throws the gyro up once",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "ジャイロを一回上に投げて"
    },
    {
      "start": 19.66,
      "end": 21.48,
      "text": "Waits for it to come back and catches it, then",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "戻ってくるのを待ってキャッチから"
    },
    {
      "start": 21.48,
      "end": 22.76,
      "text": "Comes back in with nair",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "空Nで戻ってきて"
    },
    {
      "start": 22.76,
      "end": 24.62,
      "text": "Cleanly avoids the Robo Beam",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "ロボビームをしっかり回避で"
    },
    {
      "start": 24.62,
      "end": 25.9,
      "text": "Evades and makes it back",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "いなして戻ってくる"
    },
    {
      "start": 25.9,
      "end": 28.36,
      "text": "Couldn't get the DI off on the up throw, but",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "上投げはベクトル変更間に合ってなかったけど"
    },
    {
      "start": 28.36,
      "end": 30.32,
      "text": "Hanging on with the weight advantage",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "なんとか重さで耐えている"
    },
    {
      "start": 30.32,
      "end": 34.22,
      "text": "Robo Beam",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "ja",
      "original_text": "ロボビーム"
